videos.description: Ole Miss' Stefan Moody might be the leading scorer in the SEC, but he also has some sweet passing moves, showing off the behind-the-back assist to Tomasz Gielo for the easy layup.
videos.headline: Moody shows off behind-the-back pass for easy layup
